            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">♿ Accessibility Notes</h3>
            <p>All color combinations meet WCAG 2.1 AA standards for contrast ratios. The palette includes both light and dark theme variants to accommodate different viewing preferences and reduce eye strain during extended use.</p>
